{"tid":2200814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好因為武肺痊癒率高就忽視佢嘅危險性","createTime":"2020-09-13T09:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T09:29:50.000Z","uid":30615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b18e3529e2a616bf7c4de1372840a06e05f9241f","tid":2200814,"uid":30615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=405092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405092&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Tv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=c2da339c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405092&h=d0a29470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=405092</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武肺死亡率唔算非常高係事實，死亡個案主要集中係65歲以上群組以及長期病患者亦係事實；9 成人中左武肺都會好番都係事實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但始終並唔係年輕無長期病患就可以放鬆防範，雖然類似個案唔算多，但仍然係有一部分人既後生又健康，中完武肺都元氣大傷，畢竟我地對病毒了解太少，所以一日疫苗未出黎都要繼續維持個人防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔需要過度引用啲極端例子黎誇大武肺嘅危險性（例如日日係度提武肺好番只可以起跳1cm），但亦唔好見好多人好番無事，就真係當武肺係Just a flu （引用運動員康復做例子話武肺不足為懼就更搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之祝所有巴打絲打都健健康康 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe68663cb9b91ca6abc4f41b69c592dfb442185","tid":2200814,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"拿<br />\n我就仲有幾十年先到高危<br />\n咁關我春事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒死咁啲廢老咪大家happy<br />\n要擔心都淋病擔心先啦"},{"pid":"b8b1302a6248398c0cf8bc78b827bb410ca044a8","tid":2200814,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"香港個隻中左都好似冇乜野咁"}]}